==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underaction
<hw>Un"der*ac`tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Subordinate
action; a minor action incidental or subsidiary to the main story; an
episode.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The least episodes or <qex>underactions</qex> . . . are parts
necessary or convenient to carry on the main design.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underactor</ent>⟦br⟧
